0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Steps to check the authenticity of ISO Certification"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:32:14+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Want to how to check the authenticity of ISO certification? WIZMS provides some easy steps to verify your ISO certificates legitimacy to prevent this type of"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Steps to check the authenticity of ISO Certification"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In today's world, ISO certification is a symbol of quality. ISO certification in UAE provides us with top-notch requirements for goods, services, and systems to guarantee their caliber, security, and effectiveness."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"However, there are numerous fake organizations in the business that offer fake qualifications. The ISO certificates that the buyers purchase are not even genuine. The certificates granted for ISO 9001 certification in UAE and other system standards are now only pieces of paper printed and distributed to organizations without any auditing or other means of determining if the system is actually being used or not. Several ISO certification companies in UAE that have been approved by the IAF/Non-IAF board do these operations. The significance of these fantastic quality management system standards has been destroyed by these few fake organizations."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Steps to verify ISO Certification in Dubai, UAE"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"So want to how to check the authenticity of ISO certification? WIZMS provides some easy steps to verify your ISO certificate's legitimacy to prevent this type of scam."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"1. Verify that your ISO certificate bears both an IAF mark and an accreditation logo (such as JAS-ANZ, DAC, NABCB, etc.). 2. Verify the accreditation of ISO certification companies in UAE. The independent certification of competency is offered through accreditation. Visit the International Accreditation Forum at http://www.iaf.nu to find out the ISO certification body that has received accreditation."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The IAF is an organization that brings together organizations engaged in conformity evaluation in the areas of management systems, goods and services, persons, and other projects of a similar nature. Its main goal is to provide a unified, global conformity assessment programme that lowers risk for companies and their clients by giving them confidence that authorized certifications can be trusted."}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"3. On the registrar's (the accreditation body's) website, you can check the status of the certificate. You can also speak with the certifying organisation over the phone and get confirmation that they have indeed awarded such a certificate."}],"$L2","$L3"]}],"$L4"]}]}],["$L5"],"$L6"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Therefore, choose the right ISO certification consultants in Dubai, UAE."}]
3:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms, a top-class ISO consultant in Dubai offers ISO consulting, training, implementation and ISO audit checklist services to get ISO 9001 certification. We offer ISO certification consultancy services across Abu Dhabi, Dubai, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain and Fujairah. Our ISO certification consultants in Dubai provide the best ISO certification solutions for a wide range of organizations."}]
